init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: There is panic in the streets.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: A reporter asks him why he can't just change the mugs back to where they were.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The only way to know who that really is, is to rate every dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The reporter then asks him what he is going to do about the people protesting outside.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The CEO then says, "I think I'm going to go home and visit my dad."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The CEO of the mug company was available for comments.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The reporter looked into the camera and said, "The number one mother is available to comment on that story.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Honest Mug Company is going to be just fine.
